---
title: Chicken Penne with Tomato-Spinach Cream Sauce
description: This light pasta dinner wont bog you down. Chicken roasted and slathered in creamy sun-dried tomato pesto sauce is sliced over top a creamy and zesty lemon and spinach penne pasta! It's as easy as 1, 2, 3 !
